      "date": "2012-06-18 03:18:58.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> But I wonder that why there was IGIF in lfsck test? We need more\n> investigation for that, otherwise it may be hidden the patch.\n\nTrue, as said on the Jira page, I have no idea where the file with an IGIF FID came from yet; will definitely go back to figure that out.  Thanks for the review.",
